content.rendered:
Order a system

Greeneye

Spray Less, Grow More

Turn your sprayer into a smart machine with our proprietary precision spraying system and reduce up to 90% of your herbicides usage

Order a system

Watch the world's first commercially available precision spraying system

Greeneye present the ultimate precision spraying proposal for maximum savings and efficacy

  • Reduce on average 88% of non-residual herbicides
  • Operating at a commercial travel speed of up to 15mph
  • Available for Pre & Post-emergence spraying applications
  • Precisely spray weeds with non-residual herbicides while simultaneously broadcasting residual herbicides to ensure the ultimate weed control
Interested in how our solutions can benefit your operation?
Fill out the form below, and we'll get in touch with you soon.

Spray Less, Grow More

Greeneye utilizes artificial intelligence and deep learning technology to revolutionize the weed and pest control process in agriculture, transitioning from the current practice of broadcast and wasteful spraying of herbicides and pesticides to precision spraying, reducing up to 90% of chemical usage.

Compatibility

Turn every sprayer to a smart machine

Savings

Reduce 70%-90% of non-residual herbicides

Travel speeds

Operating in commercial travel speed (15 mph)

ALL-TIME USE

Operating day and night time

Precision

Dual-spraying: Broadcast & precision work simultaneously or separately

GOB & GOG

Pre and Post emergence spraying applications

Greeneye is truly changing everything we knew about spraying herbicides, It's a Win-Win situation, I can save a substantial amount of money on my herbicides while getting much better weed control in my farm

Brad, corn grower Iowa
